 @{u}ARCHIVE@{uu}              @{u}DISCRIPTION@{uu}

 QT_BuoysB.LHA      -a set of 9 Star Fleet buoys
 QT_Travelpod.LHA   -The travelpod from the Star Trek movies
                     full detail inside and out.
 QT_DS9.LHA         -Deep Space 9 (I have 24MB and I'm
                     running out of memory rendering it)
 QT_Regula.LHA      -Regula 1 from Star Trek II
 QW_AT-PT.LHA       -AT-PT from Star Wars a two legged walker (this archive)

 Q2_dicovery1.LHA   -The Discovery 1 from 2001
 Q2_Station5.LHA    -Space Station 5 from 2001

 @{u}ON THE AMINET NOW@{uu}

 gfx/misc/IMArexxA.lha    -set of arexx scripts for Imagine 5.0
 gfx/3dobj/QT_BuoysA.LHA  -a set of 8 Star Fleet buoys



 @{u}Key@{uu}

 QT_ = quality Star Trek object
